item.title: CVE-2019-5920|2024-08-04T20:09:23.928Z -- ncrafts -- formcraft
item.description: Cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability in FormCraft 1.2.1 and earlier allows remote attackers to hijack the authentication of administrators via a specially crafted page.
